{"tid":1610821,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"螞蟻搬家，蟻多摟死象，人人有工做","createTime":"2019-10-01T21:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T11:20:22.000Z","uid":148343,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3c8e994e7a861f25f37b53c023a138c5e038bc","tid":1610821,"uid":148343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:05:56.000Z","msg":"今日係IG見到有發夢嘅人表示自己<br />\n<br />\n去到現場無所事事，唔知道可以幫啲咩<br />\n<br />\n建議文宣做宣傳嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n可以因應當時情況<br />\n<br />\n將所需物資提供在宣傳內容中<br />\n<br />\n等想出去發夢嘅人唔使兩手空空<br />\n<br />\n去到現場無所事事<br />\n<br />\n1.蟻后&rarr;前線人員<br />\n<br />\n2.雄蟻（急救人員或義工）&rarr;幫助前線人員收集所需物資（例：火魔魔法材料）<br />\n<br />\n3.工蟻（急救人員或義工）&rarr;收集兵蟻所提供嘅物資，進行分類（物資收集）<br />\n<br />\n4.兵蟻（和理非）&rarr;幫手提供物資（可以發夢前係屋企帶定，放書包）時間允許下，可以多次往返現場，盡責做一個運送兵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TPRb4pE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTPRb4pE.jpg&h=4aad015b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kmCnrC0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkmCnrC0.png&h=77285306&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ed4069f9abafaa022b65b98a8ff69c33a02bd7a","tid":1610821,"uid":148343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:07:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7aa92c8dfe33981179b82beac2522a51d2810cf","tid":1610821,"uid":148343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:07:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"129f4bed8a9d96a2f35d73deeee23e0785a9ab5f","tid":1610821,"uid":148343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:08:12.000Z","msg":"完全訓唔到"},{"pid":"ca70247554a988ba1989deeb0d0b82f6bc55fdeb","tid":1610821,"uid":124021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:09:48.000Z","msg":"咁31號生日嗰啲人可以帶咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":